      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">Not just prototypes</h3>
      But a new way of thinking about rapid prototyping. Based on your needs we can scale from a single designer to a full
      Alpha team.
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent"></div>
    </Fragment>
